video.title: Justice League Unlimited
video.synopsis: As humanity faces new villains, Superman, Wonder Woman, Batman and dozens of other animated superheroes create a league to combat each menace.

episodes.synopsis: A reluctant Green Arrow joins forces with the new Justice League to stop a rampaging nuclear monster in Asia.
episodes.title: Initiation

episodes.synopsis: Batman and Wonder Woman visit the fortress of Solitude on Superman's birthday, only to find him trapped by Mongul.
episodes.title: For the Man Who Has Everything

episodes.synopsis: Superman, Batman, Wonder Woman and Green Lantern are transformed into 8-year-olds in a desperate attempt to save the world from the magic of Mordred!
episodes.title: Kids' Stuff

episodes.synopsis: Wonder Woman teams up with two superpowered brothers to stop Ares's plans to escalate a European civil war into World War III.
episodes.title: Hawk and Dove

episodes.synopsis: It's musical mayhem when Batman and Zatanna join forces to save a teammate from a fate worse than death.
episodes.title: This Little Piggy

episodes.synopsis: Supergirl discovers that a series of nightmares she's having about being an assassin may be far more than just a bad dream.
episodes.title: Fearful Symmetry

episodes.synopsis: The Justice League is in an epic battle with Mordru in downtown Metropolis, but the real story is what happens to Booster Gold.
episodes.title: The Greatest Story Never Told

episodes.synopsis: Nearly two dozen heroes join forces to prevent an all-powerful android from reaching his goal: the recently reformed Lex Luthor.
episodes.title: The Return

episodes.synopsis: The Justice League meets the Ultimen, a popular group of young heroes who are about to discover their own horrifying secret origins.
episodes.title: Ultimatum

episodes.synopsis: When the entire League is helpless to stop an alien invasion, the world's only hope is the Atom, a microscopic superhero.
episodes.title: Dark Heart

episodes.synopsis: When Solomon Grundy rises from the grave, an old friend must come out of hiding and team up with the League once more.
episodes.title: Wake The Dead

episodes.synopsis: Batman, Wonder Woman and Green Lantern chase a time-traveling villain to the past, where they team up with the greatest heroes of the Old West.
episodes.title: The Once and Future Thing: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Justice League's adventures in time take them to Gotham City 40 years in the future, where they join forces with that era's Batman and his team.
episodes.title: The Once and Future Thing: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Black Canary convinces Green Arrow to help save her mentor, the Wildcat, from his involvement in an underground, superpowered fight club.
episodes.title: The Cat and The Canary

episodes.synopsis: The world's greatest escape artist needs help from the Flash in order to break a deadly enemy out of an inescapable prison on a harsh alien planet.
episodes.title: The Ties That Bind

episodes.synopsis: While Superman battles Doomsday in the heart of a volcano, Batman discovers an elaborate conspiracy to destroy the Justice League.
episodes.title: The Doomsday Sanction

episodes.synopsis: Five incarcerated supervillains are offered suspended sentences if they can steal a deadly weapon from the Justice League's satellite headquarters.
episodes.title: Task Force X

episodes.synopsis: Wonder Woman and Hawkgirl must put aside their feud and go to the depths of Tartarus when evil sorcerer Felix Faust establishes dominion over Hades.
episodes.title: The Balance

episodes.synopsis: Green Arrow and Black Canary race to stop the Question and Huntress from killing organized crime lord Tobias Whale.
episodes.title: Double Date

episodes.synopsis: Before Superman can even try to stop Lex Luthor's latest plot, he'll have to get past the world's mightiest mortal, Captain Marvel.
episodes.title: Clash

episodes.synopsis: Responding to a deep space distress call, Shayera leads her reluctant teammates Vigalante and Vixen into a deadly trap.
episodes.title: Mystery in Space

episodes.synopsis: The Question discovers a secret that threatens to shake the very foundations of the Justice League.
episodes.title: Question Authority

episodes.synopsis: To avenge a fallen comrade, Superman declares war on Cadmus.
episodes.title: Flashpoint

episodes.synopsis: With the founding members out of action, the remaining 50 heroes fight to survive Cadmus's ultimate attack on the Justice League.
episodes.title: Panic in the Sky

episodes.synopsis: With most of the Justice League incapacitated, who will be left to stand against the League's deadliest enemies?
episodes.title: Divided We Fall

episodes.synopsis: Fifty years in the future, the history of the Justice League is the key to Batman's darkest secret -- and his final destiny.
episodes.title: Epilogue

episodes.synopsis: Lex Luthor escapes from a maximum security prison, only to be invited to join Grodd's unstoppable Legion of Doom.
episodes.title: I Am Legion

episodes.synopsis: Batman is suspicious of Shayera's new boyfriend, a mysterious archaeologist with sinister ties to her Thanagarian past.
episodes.title: Shadow of the Hawk

episodes.synopsis: Supergirl, Stargirl and Green Lantern go to Skartaris, the hidden world at the Earth's core, to help free it from the rule of a brutal dictator.
episodes.title: Chaos at the Earth's Core

episodes.synopsis: Wonder Woman stumbles onto a plot to steal the powers hidden inside the 3,000-year-old frozen remains of the legendary hero Viking Prince.
episodes.title: To Another Shore

episodes.synopsis: Batman and Orion see a different side of the Flash when a rogue's gallery of villains attacks the museum that is opening in the Flash's honor.
episodes.title: Flash and Substance

episodes.synopsis: The ghost of a circus performer convinces Superman, Batman and Wonder Woman to help him retrieve the stolen souls of a mystic order of monks.
episodes.title: Dead Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: When an out-of-control super soldier threatens Metropolis, Green Arrow leads seven non-powered Justice Leaguers in a battle they can't hope to win.
episodes.title: Patriot Act

episodes.synopsis: A mystical accident leads to Lex Luthor and the Flash's minds being swapped.
episodes.title: The Great Brain Robbery

episodes.synopsis: Roulette starts Metabrawl again, this time with an all-female fight card made up of Justice Leaguers.
episodes.title: Grudge Match

episodes.synopsis: Supergirl, Green Lantern and Green Arrow travel into the future, where they meet the Legion of Super Heroes and their enemies, the Fatal Five.
episodes.title: Far from Home

episodes.synopsis: The Shadow Thief returns, and so does Hawkman, as more mysteries from Shadow of the Hawk are explored.
episodes.title: Ancient History

episodes.synopsis: In a devastating battle, the power behind the villains is revealed, leading to the most unexpected team-up in Justice League history. Part 1 of 2.
episodes.title: Alive!

episodes.synopsis: In a devastating battle, the power behind the villains is revealed, leading to the most unexpected team-up in Justice League history. Part 2 of 2.
episodes.title: Destroyer
